pageContext.claim: “[Maggie Haberman] likes to pretend as if she’s on the inside. She has a picture with me like so many people do, but I haven't talked to her in over a year, maybe even longer.”
pageContext.analysis: New York Times reporter Maggie Haberman consistently has some of the most incite into what is happening at the White House. The president has called her personal cell phone and gave her an exclusive interview as recently as February 2019.
